---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="About, Jeff Mills"
  description="Principal-level front-end engineer with 20+ years building enterprise web platforms, design systems, and AI-integrated product experiences."
>
  <h1 class="page-title">about</h1>

  <hr class="jm-rule" />

  <div class="about-prose">
    <p>
      I'm Jeff, a Principal-level Front-End Engineer with 20+ years of
      experience, first across fast-moving Philadelphia agencies and then at
      Vanguard. I architected
      the framework-agnostic design system that powers 11 product
      teams and the firm's main advisor portal, and I lead the
      engineering teams behind the design system and Expert Insights,
      Vanguard's AI-driven portfolio analysis platform that reached
      110,000 financial advisors on launch in April 2026.
    </p>

    <p>
      The agency years made me fast, and Vanguard taught me how to build for
      scale. What I keep coming back to is durable abstractions, the design
      decisions that hold up across platform shifts you never saw coming. The
      Vue-to-Web-Components approach I built years ago ended up becoming the
      foundation for generative-UI work none of us had imagined at the time.
    </p>

    <p>
      I work player-coach style: I write code alongside the engineers I lead,
      pair-program through the hard parts, and stay close to the production
      codebase. Lately that means a lot of AI-assisted coding with Claude,
      including a two-month team refactor from Vue to Lit and a Gen UI
      prototype I built.
    </p>

    <p class="about-locale">
      <span class="jm-badge">&gt;</span>Based in the Philadelphia area.
    </p>
  </div>

  <hr class="jm-rule" />

  <p class="about-cta">
    Open to Principal Front-End roles. <a href="mailto:jeffy9@gmail.com">say hello</a>
    &middot; <a href="/resume">read resume</a>
    &middot; <a href="https://github.com/k0bura">github.com/k0bura</a>
  </p>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    text-transform: lowercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-prose p {
    margin: 0 0 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .about-prose p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-prose code {
    font-size: 0.9em;
  }

  .about-locale {
    color: var(--jm-color-muted);
  }

  .about-locale .jm-badge {
    color: var(--jm-color-muted);
  }

  .about-cta {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--jm-color-muted);
    font-size: 0.95em;
  }
</style>
